" /><br />\n一定後悔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"有咩好後悔 香港遲早變支那其中一個城市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"後悔點解係賣樓而唔係加按用舊錢買加拿大屋再租香港果層俾人幫手供<br />\n唔係後悔點解移民, 移民係一定唔會後悔"},{"pid":"4ae5c21ec792a15345f0702f9017cae93fdb5231","tid":2073105,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T02:01:35.000Z","msg":"PEI我覺得真係太鄉下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}